			<h2 class="excerpt">当然，如果你有美腿一双，爱穿啥穿啥，你开心就好。</h2>
		<div class="detail">
				<p class="">“拿男友的衣服来穿”这件事，上至衬衫夹克，下至牛仔裤，都已经不是什么新鲜的时髦人指南了。自从当年的汤嫂 Katie Holmes 穿着阿汤哥的牛仔裤出门，掐指一算 8 年过去，Boyfriend Jeans 已经变成酷女孩几乎人手一条的经典单品了。</p><p class="">随性、慵懒、一年四季都适用，那也要好好搭配，扬长避短。</p><h2>把衣服塞进裤子里不再是小学生的专利啦</h2><div class="com-insert-images"><figure class="placeholder"></figure><figure style="margin:0;">
    <img src="/uploads/image/201602/78831872e3a7.jpg" alt="" class="">
<figcaption class="">图片来自&nbsp;<a href="http://www.likefreshlaundry.com/dressing-fourth/" style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Like fresh laundry</a>、<a href="http://www.stylepinner.com/street-style-jeans/c3RyZWV0LXN0eWxlLWplYW5z/" style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Stylepinner</a>、&nbsp;<a href="http://www.telegraph.co.uk/fashion/style/how-to-style-boyfriend-jeans-in-a-grown-up-way/">Telegraph</a></figcaption></figure></div><p class="">Boyfriend Jeans 宽松随性，但也多为低腰款，虽然能遮肉，但是裤腿肥大。如果你自认不是比例好的长腿星人，就乖乖把衣服塞进裤子里去吧，这个法则适用于衬衫、短袖 T、高领毛衣。不仅是显腿长的问题，整体 look 看起来也会更精神。</p><div class="com-insert-images"><figure class="">
    <img src="/uploads/image/201602/d07807b68d6c.jpg" alt="" class="">
<figcaption class=""><div style="text-align: center;">图片来自&nbsp;<a href="http://www.fashioninspo.com/street-fashion/best-street-style-looks-from-milan-fashion-week/" style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Fashion Inspo</a></div></figcaption></figure></div><p class="">春夏搭露胃装会是一个不错的选择，前提是你没有小肚腩。</p><h2>真正的勇士敢于直面卷裤脚的寒冷</h2><div class="com-insert-images"><figure style="margin:0;">
    <img src="/uploads/image/201602/c85bec17b02e.jpg" alt="" class="">
<figcaption class=""><div style="text-align: center;">图片来自&nbsp;<a href="http://streetstyle.allwomenstalk.com/street-style-ways-to-wear-boyfriend-jeans/6" style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">allwomenstalk</a>、<a href="http://en.louloumagazine.com/street-style/street-style-mom-et-boyfriend-jeans/" style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">LOULOU</a></div></figcaption></figure></div><p class="">“腿不够长，卷裤脚来凑”</p><p class="">从对比图可以看出，露出一截脚脖子在视觉上感觉更舒服，扬长避短。卷裤脚也更适合直筒牛仔裤在版型上的发挥。</p><p class="">如果是冬天，可以选择左图的搭配（浅口鞋+中筒袜）保护好自己的脚踝。</p><h2>把你好看的脚背露出来</h2><div class="com-insert-images"><figure style="margin:0;">
    <img src="/uploads/image/201602/610f6f82b75c.jpg" alt="" class="">
<figcaption class=""><div style="text-align: center;">图片来自&nbsp;<a href="http://justthedesign.tumblr.com/post/114211651048/arielle-nachami-is-wearing-skinny-boyfriend-jeans-from" style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Just the design</a>、<a href="http://www.whoknowsfashion.com/2014/04/04/wkfs-fashion-friday-take-slouch-in-the-boyfriend-jeans/" style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Who Knows Fashion</a></div></figcaption></figure></div><p class="">除了万年不出错的小白鞋之外，街拍中最常和 Boyfriend jeans 一起出现的，就是高跟鞋。高跟鞋可以挽救松垮牛仔裤带来的腿长劣势，拉长下半身的比例。但是呢，记得一定要大面积地露出脚背。</p><p class="">像右图大表姐这样用靴子塞得满满当当是不是就不如左图 Arielle Nachami 来得清爽？</p><div class="com-insert-images"><figure style="margin:0;">
    <img src="/uploads/image/201602/aa1a05a2c4ed.jpg" alt="" class="">
<figcaption class=""><div style="text-align: center;">图片来自&nbsp;<a href="http://justthedesign.tumblr.com/post/122091143583/another-classic-boyfriend-jeans-look-white-tee-jeans" style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Just the design</a></div></figcaption></figure></div><p class="">可以选择的搭配有尖头高跟鞋、玛丽珍鞋或是一字鞋。露出脚背可以防止下半身太过沉闷。</p><h2>啊，你会需要一条丝巾</h2><div class="com-insert-images"><figure class="">
    <img src="/uploads/image/201602/393062f0f484.jpg" alt="" class="">
</figure><figure style="margin:0;">
    <img src="/uploads/image/201602/eeb7533c9718.jpg" alt="" class="">
<figcaption class=""><div style="text-align: center;">图片来自&nbsp;<a href="http://www.telegraph.co.uk/fashion/style/how-to-style-boyfriend-jeans-in-a-grown-up-way/" style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Telegraph</a></div></figcaption></figure></div><p class="">Boyfriend jeans 腰身通常很低，差不多在胯部的位置，因此如果配普通的皮带，常常会在后腰的地方拱起来，不好看。一条丝巾就可以完美解决这个问题，还够特别。</p><p class="">事实上，配饰很重要，如果你全身的单品都走简洁风没什么心机，那么一款特别的包袋、首饰或是丝巾会很加分。</p><h2>至于上装，丰俭由人</h2><div class="com-insert-images"><figure class="placeholder"></figure><figure class="">
    <img src="/uploads/image/201602/2abb548f463e.jpg" alt="" class="">
<figcaption class=""><p style="text-align: center;">图片来自&nbsp;<a href="http://www.thefashionspot.com/style-trends/613743-how-to-wear-boyfriend-jeans/#/slide/1">The Fashion Spot</a></p></figcaption></figure></div><p class="">

Boyfriend jeans 的最大特质就在于，无论上装搭配得多么繁复，搭上一条牛仔裤就能瞬间变得简洁。&nbsp;
</p><p class="">上装的选择实际上没什么局限性，最简单的单品，比如白色 T 恤、条纹衫、西装上衣、印花衬衫都不太会出错，如果想要出彩，可以试试和牛仔裤同色系的牛仔上衣，或者对比感更强的皮衣。<br></p><div class="com-insert-images"><figure class="">
    <img src="/uploads/image/201602/fa81cffcb6c6.jpg" alt="" class="">
<figcaption class=""><div style="text-align: center;">&nbsp; 图片来自&nbsp;<a href="http://www.thefashionspot.com/style-trends/613743-how-to-wear-boyfriend-jeans/#/slide/1" style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">The Fashion Spot</a></div></figcaption></figure></div><p class="">题图来自<a href="http://themirroronthewall.com/spring-fashion-trend-stripes/" style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">The mirror on the wall</a></p>
		</div>
	</div>
	<div class="article-detail-ft">
